stories}{\fs22\lang11274\langfe3082\langnp11274  (historias), y }{\i\fs22\lang11274\langfe3082\langnp11274 story }{\fs22\lang11274\langfe3082\langnp11274 (historia) es simplemente una forma abreviada de }{\i\fs22\lang11274\langfe3082\langnp11274 history}{
