The Fellowship of the Ring}{\fs22\lang11274\langfe3082\langnp11274  (\'93La cofrad\'eda del anillo\'94), el segundo, }{\i\fs22\lang11274\langfe3082\langnp11274 The Two Towers}{\fs22\lang11274\langfe3082\langnp11274  (\'93Las dos torres\'94
